org.sensorhub.test.persistence

Class AbstractTestObsStorage<StorageType extends IObsStorageModule<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.test.persistence.AbstractTestBasicStorage<StorageType>
      • org.sensorhub.test.persistence.AbstractTestObsStorage<StorageType>
  • Type Parameters:
    StorageType - type of storage under test
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractTestMultiObsStorage, TestPerstObsStorage

    public abstract class AbstractTestObsStorage<StorageType extends IObsStorageModule<?>>
extends AbstractTestBasicStorage<StorageType>

    Abstract base for testing implementations of IObsStorage. The storage needs to be correctly instianted by derived tests in a method tagged with '@Before'.
